module_connect_description: Plug in and power up the required module(s) via the OT-2 USB Ports. Place the modules as show in the deck map.
module_connect_duplicate_description: Duplicate modules should be plugged in to the USB ports with the lowest deck slot number corresponding to the left-most USB port. Check out our help docs for more information on using duplicate modules.
module_connect_missing_tooltip: Connect module(s) to proceed to labware calibration
modules_update_software_tooltip: Update robot software to see USB port information
